node.text: During these tough times, it is even more important to be grateful for all the fathers and father figures who have made a big impact in our lives.  Today and always I’m grateful for @donfelipemuniz for all the sacrifices he made for our family, for the example he set, and for the gift of music. Te amo!  Little Tony ❤️
